long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
IncognitoThis is a Chrome/Chromium extension for instantly opening the current tab in an incognito window and vice-versa!

It is completely free and open-source. Contributions welcome! - https://github.com/chinnichaitanya/IncognitoThis/
